data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to 2837 Lafayette Trace Drive- an incredibly well maintained home where all of the heavy lifting has been done for you- NEW ROOF 2023, NEWER AC, SALT WATER POOL WITH NEW PUMP AND FILTER. With over 3300 sq ft, this 5 bedroom, 4 bathroom floorplan offers plenty of room to spread out or grow into. Through the front doors, you are greeted with a traditional dining room to the left and an office or flex space to the right. 10 ft TALL CEILINGS, 8 ft TALL DOORS and CERAMIC TILE will follow you throughout the common areas of the home.   A functional kitchen with 42” CABINETS, GRANITE countertops, and KENMORE appliances make cooking while entertaining a breeze, transferring food back into the formal dining room, snacking at the breakfast nook, or staying part of the fun in the family room. This 3 way split floor plan starts with the Master Bedroom up front, with room for large furniture and even a seating area if desired and flows out to the pool. The Bathroom suite has dual sinks, separate shower and tub, and a HUGE WALK IN CLOSET with CUSTOM SHELVING. 2 beds + bath in the middle of the home with a full bed and bath suite towards the back of the home. That bathroom doubles as a pool bath, perfectly located to prevent the wet ones from trudging through the house after playing in the pool.    The abundance of space continues upstairs with a space that caters to whatever you need it to be: a gym, a theatre room, a kids play room, craft area- the flexibility provides endless opportunities. Through the flex room you will find an extra large 5th bedroom and bath suite- an awesome option for extra privacy for overnight guests or even an excellent scenario for multigenerational living.  The best part of this home is the pool area! The epitome of Florida living- offering a covered and screened in lanai and gorgeous WATER VIEWS. This salt water pool has a new pump, a newer filter, the pool lining is still in great condition and heating the pool is all done by solar panels. Finishing us off is a fenced in backyard to keep our furry friends in or even the kiddos safe inside. Stevens Plantation is a master planned community situated in a super convenient location in St Cloud- known for it’s tree lined streets and family friendly atmosphere with well maintained sidewalks, lush green spaces and a strong sense of community. It features excellent schools, easy access to Florida’s turnpike to get you to all the popular Orlando destinations. Easy to see. Call for your private tour today. Check out the Matterport and Video tour, too!
